-align: baseline;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Prvi dan, 15. mart 2013.</strong></u></span></div>\n	<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		&nbsp;</div>\n	<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		<h3 style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(14, 86, 114); font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; line-height: 22px; list-style-type: none; text-align: center;">\n			<span style="font-size:14px;"><strong>Dan za preduzetnike i privredu</strong></span></h3>\n		<ul style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none outside; font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; color: rgb(14, 86, 114); line-height: 22px;">\n			<li style="color: inherit; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.625;">\n				09:00 &ndash; 11:00 /&nbsp;<strong style="color: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.625;">Registracija</strong></li>\n			<li style="color: inherit; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.625;">\n				11:00 &ndash; 11:20 /&nbsp;<strong style="color: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.625;">Svečano otvaranje</strong></li>\n			<li style="color: inherit; font-size: 15px; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.625;">\n				11:20 &ndash; 11:50 /&nbsp;<strong style="color: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.625;">Web prodaje</strong><br style="color: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.625;" />\n				Miloje Sekulić, Internet i poslovni konsultant. Vlasnik konsultantske&nbsp;<a data-mce-="" href="http://www.internetagencija.rs/" style="color: rgb(27, 139, 224); font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.625; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">Internet