(297, 80, 167, 'nikola7383', 'Technobank 2013', '<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 18px;">\n	<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Technobank 2013. konferencija i izložba bankarske tehnologije</strong>&nbsp;održaće se 1<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">0. i 11. aprila u hotelu Metropol Palace u Beogradu</strong>. Ovogodi&scaron;nji&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Technobank će se&nbsp;</strong>fokusirati na najnovije raspoložive tehnologije u regionu i &scaron;ire i njihovoj primeni na ovim trži&scaron;tima. Takođe, ovogodi&scaron;nje teme će se baviti i novim učesnicima na platnom trži&scaron;tu &ndash; kao &scaron;to su mobilni operateri ili veliki maloprodajni lanci. Na konferenciji će učestvovati eksperti iz zemlje i inostranstva koji će ponuditi prezentacije najnovijih re&scaron;enja kao i studije slučaja u oblasti novih platnih tehnologija.</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 18px;">\n	Najnovije tehnologije, kao &scaron;to su NFC beskontaktne tehnologije, kori&scaron;ćenje mobilnog telefona kao sredstva plaćanja, sistemi javnog prevoza, lojalti &scaron;eme, primena prepaid kartica, cloud computing i nova dokument-menadžment re&scaron;enja će biti prezentovane tokom rada Konferencije. I ove godine&nbsp;specijalizovani forum -&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">CARD FORUM &amp; EXPO 2013</strong>, potpuno posvećen platnim transakcijama putem bankarskih kartica i podržanim ICT tehnologijama u Evropi i svetu, biće održan tokom Technobank Konferencije.</p>\n<h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-size: 25px; font-family: muzeo, ''Trebuchet MS'', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">\n	<cufon alt="Agenda" class="cufon cufon-canvas" style="width: 90px; height: 25px; display: inline-block !important; position: relative !important; vertical-align: middle !important; font-size: 1px !important; line-height: 1px !important;"><canvas height="28" style="position: relative !important; width: 102px; height: 28px; top: -3px; left: -1px;" width="102"></canvas><cufontext style="display: inline-block !important; width: 0px !important; height: 0px !important; overflow: hidden !important; text-indent: -10000in !important;"></cufontext></cufon></h2>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 18px;">\n	<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Technobank 2013 Konferencije</strong></p>\n<ul style="margin: 0px 0px 15px 12px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 17px;">\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Business Continuity Management (BCM) &ndash; Business Continuity Planning (BCP) i Disaster Recovery (DR)</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Upravljanje poslovnim procesima</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Računarstvo u oblacima (Cloud Computing)</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Dru&scaron;tvene mreže</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Data centri</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Mobilna telefonija četvrte generacije</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Mobline aplikacije u poslovanju</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Upravljanje rizicima i naplata potraživanja</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Identity and Access Management sistemi</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Customer Relationship Management (CRM) and Contact Center (CC) technologies</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Digitalno arhiviranje i sistemi upravljanja dokumentacijom</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		ICT bezbednosni aspekti u bankama</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Standardizacija sistema bezbednosti u bankarskim operacijama (ISO/IEC 27001:2005)</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Nove vizije identifikacije i autentifikacije korisnika banaka &ndash; moguće kori&scaron;ćenje biometrijskih tehnika</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Re&scaron;enja protiv krađe identiteta</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Savremene ICT bankarske infrastrukture</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Novosti u tehnologijama plaćanja i operacija</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Fizička i tehnička bezbednost u bankarskom okruženju &ndash; nova re&scaron;enja</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Osiguravajuća dru&scaron;tva i novi vidovi osiguranja</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Business Intelligence (BI) i Management Information Systems (MIS)</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Novi aspekti home banking i e-banking sistema</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Kreditni biroi</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Druga inovativna bankarska re&scaron;enja i primeri najbolje prakse</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style="margin: 20px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">\n	<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">CARD FORUM &amp; EXPO 2013</strong></h3>\n<ul style="margin: 0px 0px 15px 12px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 17px;">\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		EMV i non-EMV kontaktni i beskontaktni platni sistemi</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Beskontaktni POS terminali</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		NFC (Near Field Communications) platne tehnologije</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		M-banking i M-payment sistemi</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Sistemi multiaplikativnih platnih kartica</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Kartice lojaliteta, poklon kartice i kartice sa slikama</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		CAP i DPA EMV sistemi dinamičkih lozinki</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		CAP/DPA connected/unconnected čitaci smart kartica</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Access Control Server 3D secure sistemi &ndash; inhouse ili outsource?</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Neki aspekti EMV migracije</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Aspekti procesiranja kartica</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Aspekti personalizacije i proizvodnje kartica</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Instant issuance sistemi</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Bezbednosni aspekti platnih kartica</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		PCI (Payment Card Industry) bezbednosni standard</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		E-commerce sistemi</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		3D Security sistem za bezbedne e-commerce sisteme</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Nove platne aplikacije</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Novi aspekti u tehnologijama POS terminala i bankomata</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		SEPA okvir</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		E-purse sistemi i &scaron;eme lojaliteta</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Prevencija pronevera i upravljanje rizikom</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Regionalna saradnja između banaka i drugih finansijskih institucija</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Specifičnosti regionalnog trži&scaron;ta &ndash; pretnje i mogućnosti</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style="margin: 20px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">\n	<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">SECURITY</strong></h3>\n<ul style="margin: 0px 0px 15px 12px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 17px;">\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		IT Security strategy</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		IT &amp; users &ndash; new IT devices that are not corporative, mobility, tablets &ndash;from the point of security</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Applying &amp; security solutions implementation</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Nowadays Cyber threts, evolution, challenges, protection</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Virtual surrounding security &ndash; differences and challenges compared to classic systems</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Cloud security &ndash; security in the cloud and out</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Consciousness about security in Serba (Case Studies)</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Security from the point of view of security exspert</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Security from the point of view of security user</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Security from the point of view of security hacker</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Solutions against identity theft</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style="margin: 20px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">\n	<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">OKRUGLI STOLOVI</strong></h3>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 18px;">\n	Tokom Technobank 2013 Konferencije, biće organizovani Okrugli stolovi sa sledećim temama koje se bave najnovijim trendovima: 1.&nbsp;Mobilna plaćanja u kombinaciji sa NFC tehnologijom &ndash; jedan&nbsp;od najznačajnijih alata za razvoj i inovacije?, 2. Da li su se eGovernment inicijative pojavile kao ključna podr&scaron;ka bezgotovinskom plaćanju?, 3. Pitanja regulative u evropskom sektoru platnih tehnologija, posebno u industriji platnih kartica.</p>\n<h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-size: 25px; font-family: muzeo, ''Trebuchet MS'', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">\n	<cufon alt="Registracija" class="cufon cufon-canvas" style="width: 134px; height: 25px; display: inline-block !important; position: relative !important; vertical-align: middle !important; font-size: 1px !important; line-height: 1px !important;"><canvas height="28" style="position: relative !important; width: 146px; height: 28px; top: -3px; left: -1px;" width="146"></canvas><cufontext style="display: inline-block !important; width: 0px !important; height: 0px !important; overflow: hidden !important; text-indent: -10000in !important;"></cufontext></cufon></h2>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 18px;">\n	Vi&scaron;e o cenama i registraciji za učesnike možete naći&nbsp;<a href="http://www.technobank.rs/rs/participants.html" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(40, 101, 166);">ovde</a>, dok potencijalni izlagači dodatne informacije mogu pronaći&nbsp;<a href="http://www.technobank.rs/rs/exhibitors.html" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(40, 101, 166);">ovde</a>.</p>\n', 'Conference ', NULL, 'logo_504.jpg', 1363833227, 1365573600, 1365710400, 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PteNlLEK4zw', '', 1, NULL, NULL, 'background_events297.JPG', NULL, '', '', 'technobank', 1, ''),
(301, 80, 169, 'nikola7383', 'Tvitomanija', '<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 18px;">\n	<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Tvitomanija&nbsp;2013</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; najveća regionalna konferencija posvećena dru&scaron;tvenim mrežama, održaće se&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">od 8. do 12. maja&nbsp;</strong>u<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">hotelu&nbsp;NOVI Spa Hotels &amp; Resort&nbsp;u Novom Vinodolskom, u Hrvatskoj.</strong>&nbsp;Tema druge po redu Tvitomanije je&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">&bdquo;Dru&scaron;tvene mreže i život&ldquo;</strong>&nbsp;i na njoj će se govoriti o svim sferama života u kojima su dru&scaron;tvene mreže napravile revoluciju &ndash; komunikacijama, sportu, medijima, obrazovanju, politici, modi, nauci, biznisu, umetnosti, estradi, kulturi&hellip;</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 18px;">\n	Cilj je da ovogodi&scaron;nja Tvitomanija na jednom mestu, na hrvatskom primorju, okupi preko hiljadu korisnika popularnih dru&scaron;tvenih mreža. Istih onih dru&scaron;tvenih mreža koje su praktično izjednačile anonimuse sa poznatim ličnostima, preduzetnike i korporacije, narod i političare, offline i online medije, i koje su nam omogućile dvosmernu komunikaciju sa svim tim ljudima koji utiču na na&scaron; svakodnevni život i čine ga&hellip; pa svakako zanimljivijim.&nbsp;Otvoren je poziv za digitalne, marketin&scaron;ke, PR i ostale kreativne agencije, kao i male, srednje i velike kompanije da predstave svoje najuspe&scaron;nije projekte i kampanje.</p>\n<h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-size: 25px; font-family: muzeo, ''Trebuchet MS'', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">\n	<cufon alt="Program" class="cufon cufon-canvas" style="width: 102px; height: 25px; display: inline-block !important; position: relative !important; vertical-align: middle !important; font-size: 1px !important; line-height: 1px !important;"><canvas height="28" style="position: relative !important; width: 104px; height: 28px; top: -3px; left: -1px;" width="104"></canvas><cufontext style="display: inline-block !important; width: 0px !important; height: 0px !important; overflow: hidden !important; text-indent: -10000in !important;"></cufontext></cufon></h2>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 18px;">\n	Na Tvitomaniji će se u okviru&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">predavanja, panel diskusija i radionica</strong>&nbsp;govoriti o prednostima koje pojedincima i kompanijama donosi aktivno i kvalitetno prisustvo na dru&scaron;tvenim mrežama. Poznate ličnosti, predstavnici malih i velikih kompanija i stručnjaci za komunikaciju će razgovarati o tome kako se predstavljati na popularnim dru&scaron;tvenim mrežama, i na koje sve načine&nbsp;Twitter,Facebook,&nbsp;YouTube,&nbsp;Instagram,&nbsp;Foursquare,&nbsp;Pinterest,&nbsp;Tumblr&nbsp;i mnoge druge dru&scaron;tvene mreže mogu pomoći da se kvalitetno pozicionirate u sve &scaron;iroj Internet zajednici.</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 18px;">\n	Dok se ne formira konačni program, ovo su&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">neke od tematskih oblasti</strong>&nbsp;ovogodi&scaron;nje Tvitomanije:</p>\n<ul style="margin: 0px 0px 15px 12px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 17px;">\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Mediji na dru&scaron;tvenim mrežama</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		PRimeri dobre i lo&scaron;e komunikacije</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Državna uprava na Tviteru</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Javne ličnosti na dru&scaron;tvenim mrežama</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Kratak kurs o &ldquo;uticaju&rdquo; ili &ldquo;How to get ATTENTION without becoming a whore!&ldquo;</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Dru&scaron;tvene mreže u funkciji (re)integracije regiona</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Dru&scaron;tvene mreže i povratak bloga</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Viralne akcije na dru&scaron;tvenim mrežama</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Dru&scaron;tvene mreže na mobilnim telefonima i tabletima</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Fotografija i dru&scaron;tvene mreže</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Servisi za praćenje dru&scaron;tvenih mreža</li>\n</ul>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 18px;">\n	Biće organizovano i&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">NEtakmičenje</strong>, na kojem se neće deliti nagrade, ali će seobratiti pažnja na najbolje primere u sledećim kategorijama:</p>\n<ul style="margin: 0px 0px 15px 12px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 17px;">\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Nastup malih i srednjih preduzeća na dru&scaron;tvenim mrežama</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Korporativno prisustvo na dru&scaron;tvenim mrežama</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Odgovorno dru&scaron;tvo na dru&scaron;tvenim mrežama</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Najuticajnije kampanje digitalnih agencija</li>\n</ul>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 18px;">\n	Pored zvaničnog dela konferencije očekuje se i bogat prateći program, sa naglaskom na zabavu do sitnih sati, po uzoru na visoke standarde koji su postavljeni na Blogomaniji.</p>\n<h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-size: 25px; font-family: muzeo, ''Trebuchet MS'', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">\n	<cufon alt="Učesnici" class="cufon cufon-canvas" style="width: 100px; height: 25px; display: inline-block !important; position: relative !important; vertical-align: middle !important; font-size: 1px !important; line-height: 1px !important;"><canvas height="28" style="position: relative !important; width: 120px; height: 28px; top: -3px; left: -1px;" width="120"></canvas><cufontext style="display: inline-block !important; width: 0px !important; height: 0px !important; overflow: hidden !important; text-indent: -10000in !important;"></cufontext></cufon></h2>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 18px;">\n	Možete pogledati ko su učesnici Tvitomanije na ovom&nbsp;<a href="http://tvitomanija.me/ucesnici/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(40, 101, 166);">linku.</a></p>\n<h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-size: 25px; font-family: muzeo, ''Trebuchet MS'', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">\n	<cufon alt="Lokacija" class="cufon cufon-canvas" style="width: 96px; height: 25px; display: inline-block !important; position: relative !important; vertical-align: middle !important; font-size: 1px !important; line-height: 1px !important;"><canvas height="28" style="position: relative !important; width: 108px; height: 28px; top: -3px; left: -1px;" width="108"></canvas><cufontext style="display: inline-block !important; width: 0px !important; height: 0px !important; overflow: hidden !important; text-indent: -10000in !important;"></cufontext></cufon></h2>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 18px;">\n	Ove godine regionalna Tvitomanija održaće se u&nbsp;&nbsp;hotelu&nbsp;NOVI Spa Hotels &amp; Resort&nbsp;u Novom Vinodolskom, u Hrvatskoj. Kako doći do hotela avionom, busom, kolima &nbsp;iz Srbije, Slovenije, Hrvatske, Bosne i Hercegovine&hellip;.možete pogledati<a href="http://tvitomanija.me/lokacija/" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(40, 101, 166);">&nbsp;ovde.</a></p>\n<h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-size: 25px; font-family: muzeo, ''Trebuchet MS'', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">\n	<cufon alt="Registracija" class="cufon cufon-canvas" style="width: 134px; height: 25px; display: inline-block !important; position: relative !important; vertical-align: