(140, 80, 'nikola7383', 'Restoran Reka', 'Restoran Reka', '<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\n	Od svih poku&scaron;aja da se napi&scaron;e, kraća, duža, efektna, duhovita... istorija REKE nama se najvi&scaron;e dopalo Stankovo pismo :</div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\n	&quot;Draga Reko,</div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\n	Verovao sam u tebe jo&scaron; dok si bila samo malo ribolovačko alkoholičarsko kafanče u ćo&scaron;ku Zemuna. Verovao i bio često uz tebe. Čak i če&scaron;će no &scaron;to je trebalo. Ne obazirući se na dosadno zvocanje moje jetre i ostalih organa iz unutra&scaron;njosti. A vidi je sada...prava velika kafana za koju su čuli čak i u Zambiji.</div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\n	Sretan ti rođendan sa željom &nbsp;da i dalje raste&scaron;, i da ti ba&scaron;ta izraste čak do Lida, na radost tvojih mama.</div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\n	<strong>Tvoj čika Stanko</strong></div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div style="text-align: justify;">\n	&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n	<p style="text-align: justify;">\n		&nbsp;</p>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		IZ KNJIGE UTISAKA:</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		&nbsp;</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		&quot;Ljudi, ovde je fenomanolno! &quot;La luna&quot; je moj najomiljeniji bend i rado ih gledamo uvek kada dodjemo iz Nemacke!&quot;</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		Marija i Sasa iz Kelna</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		Super, sve pohvale! Od usluge preko ostalog!!!</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		Zeljko, Phoenix</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		Joj ,kak je lijepo kod vas!!!Samo tako nastavite!Pozdrav od purgera!!!!Puse...</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		&quot;Bili ste odlicni!!! Naravili ste sjajnu atmosferu!&quot;</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		Dijana R.</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		14.04.2012.</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		Hvala na prekrasno provedenoj veceri, redak dozivljaj i posebno na usluzi ljubaznoj Vesni i Fati.</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		Arhitekta Ceda Popovic</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		&nbsp;</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		&quot;Reka, mesto koje ima najvecu dusu u Bgd...ne bih mogla doci u ovaj grad, a da bar jedno vece ne dodjem....Divno vece ovo uskrsnje vece...Milena &quot;La luna&quot; &nbsp;i ekipa, pa to je retkost...Sve ove pesme...iz sveg srca...Hvala&quot;</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		&nbsp;Svetlana Zeneva</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		Sandra &quot;Sluzbeni glasnik&quot;</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		Svetlana B. Beograd</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;&sbquo;</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		&nbsp;</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		&quot;Zamerka nema placanja karticama koje nisu Dina. Obavezno to popraviti!!!&quot;</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		&nbsp;</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		&quot;Katastrofa, nema narodnjaka.&quot; Slavica</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		&nbsp;</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		&quot;Puno pozdrava od Banjalucana.Extra ste!!!&quot; Buki i Veki</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		&nbsp;</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		&quot; Da je &quot;Reka&quot; Parizu, ja bih Pariz voljela jos vise! &quot;Reka&quot;, &quot;Reka&quot; cool mjesto, omiljena adresa...nemam rijeci, uvek kada izadjem kroz &nbsp;vasa zelena vrata... uspomene tek naviru kada se probudim u Zagrebu!</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		Slavila sam ovdje svoj 27. rodjendan, nadam se i 1.rodjendan svog djeteta, 25.godisnjicu braka, 100 godisnjicu...&quot;</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Hvala</div>\n	<div style="text-align: justify;">\n		&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Alma</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', 'www.reka.co.rs', 'img_1359053072.jpg', 1359053188, 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TgSqE78u9bs', '', 'Serbia', 'Beograd', 'Kej oslobodjenja 73', '', 1, 'background_venues140.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1),
(144, 80, 'nikola7383', 'Test', 'Beogradski test', '<p>\n	<span style="color: rgb(103, 103, 103); font-family: ''Open Sans'', arial, tahoma, verdana; font-size: 13px; line-height: 17px;">Novo - staro mesto. Beograđani vole ovde da izlaze, proverite za&scaron;to! Na otvaranju je nastupio Toni Cetinjski, a očekuje nas jo&scaron; mnogo kvalitetnih izvođača.</span></p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<div class="title" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(103, 103, 103); font-family: ''Open Sans'', arial, tahoma, verdana; line-height: 17px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\n	Dobar za</div>\n<ul class="goodfor" style="margin: 0px 0px 15px 2em; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(103, 103, 103); font-family: ''Open Sans'', arial, tahoma, verdana; line-height: 17px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\n		Biti viđen</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\n		Vidjanje poznatih</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\n		Upoznavanje</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\n		Muvanje</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\n		Viđanje atraktivnih ljudi</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\n		Lud provod sa prijateljima</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\n		VIP uslugu</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\n		One sa &ldquo;dubljim&rdquo; džepom</li>\n</ul>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(103, 103, 103); font-family: ''Open Sans'', arial, tahoma, verdana; line-height: 17px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\n	Nekada je F 6 bio sinonim dobrog provoda . Sada je ponovi tako, jer ovaj legendardni beogradski klub, nakon nekoliko godina mirovanja doživeo<i style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">&nbsp;re - opening</i>. I to kakav.</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(103, 103, 103); font-family: ''Open Sans'', arial, tahoma, verdana; line-height: 17px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\n	Iako je potpuno renoviran zadržao je deo starog prepoznatljivog &scaron;meka,sa dobrom atmosferom I jo&scaron; boljom ekipom. Ovde ne dolaze klinci, već oni malo ozbiljniji, koji znaju &scaron;ta je dobar provod.</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(103, 103, 103); font-family: ''Open Sans'', arial, tahoma, verdana; line-height: 17px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\n	Muzika koja se pu&scaron;ta je pop i rok zvuku a najavljeni su nastupi bendova poput Ekstra Orkestre, Olje i Shirkana kao i izvođača Tonija Cetinskog, Željka Vasića, Nine Badrić i drugih.</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(103, 103, 103); font-family: ''Open Sans'', arial, tahoma, verdana; line-height: 17px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\n	Ovde dolaze i poznati: Bojana Stojković, Danijela Jankov, Marija Kilibarda...</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n', 'walltoall.com', 'img_1362243470.jpg', 1362243492, 'http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BQuWli6Hn1I', '', 'Srbija', 'Beograd', 'Francuska 6', '', 1, 'background_venues144.jpg', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1),
